OL,2,MSo AIs are lying to us now, huh?
OL,4,CMatthew Wearden
OL,5,CSat 17:50-18:20
OL,6,CStage A
OL,8,GAs AI systems are getting smarter,
OL,9,Gsafety researchers are increasingly
OL,10,Gconcerned by a new capability of these
OL,11,Gmodels - they are getting very good at
OL,12,Glying. This behaviour is seen both in
OL,13,Gand out of evaluation settings, and
OL,14,Ghas a fascinating range of root
OL,15,Gcauses. In this talk, we'll
OL,16,Ginvestigate the phenomena of AI
OL,17,Gdeception across a broad range of
OL,18,Gscenarios. Discover how chatbots lie
OL,19,Gfor your own good, when models
OL,20,Gstrategically hide their capabilities,
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
